Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I don't have my glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.32,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}BON-BON Cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:51.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:03.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:10.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:22.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:03.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:36.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can solve this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:39.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just called on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:42.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:46.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:49.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my English textbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go borrow Kagami's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They already had English, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:06.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:09.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should double-check everything the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa tends to forget stuff a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:20.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Konata doesn't forget stuff like textbooks often.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:24.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm surprisingly diligent about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:27.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I never take my textbooks home in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not called diligent at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:35.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't review what we\Nwent over in class without a textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I never study at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:41.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you end up cramming the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kona-chan's good at putting off stuff till the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:48.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be why I forget to do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't forget to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:56.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So show me your homework for Japanese this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:57.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Already at it again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki's in your class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her to show you her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san's such a nice person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it ends up being hard to ask her for anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this sensation you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I get what you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I still can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:17.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was late because I had to help someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually go around with this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I just couldn't get away today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was like it's okay, we can split up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the other five of us had gotten one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he was the odd one out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which kinda left a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:46.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you've been in the same party for a\Nlong time, you wanna help each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we all backed him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, friends are a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were up all night playing online games again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kept playing after I logged off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:00.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl crashed into me in the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she suddenly grabbed my hand and took off running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I learned that she'd stolen some taiyaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was on the run...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what any of this had to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I had no choice but to duck into\Na café to hide from the taiyaki baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So many potential comebacks...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a teacher!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a human being!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm down with a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I need to take a sick day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much gaming again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The same trick won't work every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess. You've got a summer cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter's over and the weather's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so stop being lazy and get to class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:07.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So she totally treated me like the boy who cried wolf yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like my fever broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but my throat still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:19.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you breathe through your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can also breathe through your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but wouldn't you usually breathe through your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:26.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:30.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kona-chan breathes through her mouth more than her nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:31.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:35.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If a virus enters through your mouth, you get a throat infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:39.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And if a virus enters through your nose, you get a nasal infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:44.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So people with sore throats probably had a\Nhigher chance of a virus entering through their throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is when we turn to Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:49.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel like doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About your birthday party today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we hold it at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot that I can't move a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're baking cookies right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:12.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa and other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't abbreviate me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san and Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have presents for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Matching earrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I considered a number of options...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I had a hard time making up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are presents from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}[Caption: Chief]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Brigade chief armband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I put this on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:04.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it would fit you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It would go better on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:06.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It cost a fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:16.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to make both of us cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's barely any different from our uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:23.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:24.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could hold back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's cookies are always so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I baked them with her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda learned as I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:47.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...some of these cookies don't taste as good as the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if this is one of Kagami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:54.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well eat the cake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:58.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagamin – works hard only on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:02.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't there always a fight over how to cut the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you cut a cake into a bunch of slices...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...how do you divide up the strawberries on top...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or decide who gets the chocolate decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My older sisters all love chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't expect that from Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My strawberry's awfully small.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have cake on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:54.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just discovered another facet of Kagamin's charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound just like Shin-chan, so stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, the pool, and summer festivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other usual events?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:05.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer is all about the annual celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The beginning of the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Comiket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That only applies to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that like cricket?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their own different thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like visiting relatives or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you have some kind of regular summer activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:36.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking a vacation overseas again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:37.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She said again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid bourgeois!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that like yogurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:45.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you started working at a costume café...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:49.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need a good figure to pull that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:49.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:53.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lamenting my lack of a chest for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:54.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then this game said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"A flat chest is a status symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A rarity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Word for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:05.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...there is a demand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I'm valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to know how a line from a game can fill her with confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'm okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a test coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be gaming so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would only use some of that passion for studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grades would probably go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she's so easily influenced...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...wouldn't she become a genius if\Nsomeone released a game that promoted studying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's already stuff like Moe Drill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:35.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot of juvenile crimes lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the neighbors say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was such a nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have imagined that he could do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:48.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:53.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That just means you can't judge a person on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever commit a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I always figured she would do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot that I don't feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:15.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:19.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you never feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Making progress on your studying for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tidying up my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:45.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how kinda get the urge to start\Ncleaning when you're feeling the pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but study.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a little studying done today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:59.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a thirty minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:07.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thirty more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Haruhi about to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:29.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They definitely cut corners\Nwith those long-winded Nagato scenes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Ya***** hasn't been very impressive recently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already flaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not going to happen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to sleep and wake up early to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wake up at five...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can sleep three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:16.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up killing time yesterday by\Nreading manga and watching anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like something you would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:22.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have some odd taste in manga and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You read manga aimed at boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and mainly play dating sims for men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad reads manga and plays games a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I was probably influenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching him from the side since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can understand the manga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:39.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but playing dating sims in front of your daughter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of father is he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't your mom have anything to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...with both of you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:52.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She died when I was really little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:57.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm always doing housework...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which is why I'm way better than Kagami is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:01.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the mood isn't right for comebacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's also good at cooking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I would say that I'm good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:08.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how good Miyuki-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks rich...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so maybe she's bad at housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I only help out from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'm not very skilled at housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miyuki's so good at everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it doesn't really feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:36.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just assume that she's bad when she says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about our teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she lives by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she looks like she could be a slob.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...ya can get by without knowing how ta cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got your convenience stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:58.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About as well as your average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't make jokes that sound like they're true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa still has my dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Could I get my dictionary back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was doing a little cleaning for a change of pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:19.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:30.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The people at work are trying to\Ncome up with a new menu for summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:32.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do stuff like that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, did you give up on studying for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy stuff's good when it's hot outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so how about super spicy ramen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:43.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go with something you would usually find in a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a super spicy parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop skipping the thinking process when you respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:03.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't our school have swimming class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually relieved by that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't open my eyes underwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I can't really swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why can't I have all your "weaknesses"?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:26.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The summer Comp Festival is finally about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:32.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I started working...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You bring so many fond memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you pulling out an ancient reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When the customers start getting excited with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't it feel like everyone's\Npumped up together for the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:51.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use some of that passion on academic endeavors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having trouble getting to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I'll read until I fall asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:04.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I happen to have some stuff I just bought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for falling asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm feeling really sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:30.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand turning off your phone around priority seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of pacemakers and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:37.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do they ban cell phone use for the whole train?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll disturb other people when you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't trains already noisy with people talking anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes men and women of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:57.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to work at the temple\Nfor summer festivals like you did for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't work in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting to be that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:09.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because of all the studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I weighed myself yesterday, it was down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured it'd be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:18.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And like, you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:27.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My weight already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...went all the way up in like the blink of an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause you let go and started snacking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And wasn't that a senryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:43.43,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I only...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.16,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I only ate a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}It's not like a kilo or two\Nis going to affect how you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:52.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get so excited and depressed over every kilogram?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why women are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:10.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to another episode of Lucky Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Has everyone been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:17.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira Kogami, always running at 120%!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:17.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:18.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:22.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a kiddy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn the job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be dropped from this role?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:34.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:35.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have big news for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:47.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Published in the November issue of Comptiq...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Project Fashionable Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:54.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already received this many postcards from everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:54.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there was another person involved in that project...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all the feedback!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like cowabunga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:08.14,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't think anyone's going to understand a joke from the eighties...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:11.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll reveal the idea I've selected after extensive review.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:12.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:16.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from a Miss Cherry in Satte, Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Project Fashionable Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:23.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san's pigtails look great on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Akira-san also wore pigtails?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pigtails, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair styling is a woman's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I split it in two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:38.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it might look lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No ifs or buts about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:43.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it impossible with your hair length...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like long hair is always a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Akira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.14,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's really gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It weighs a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:53.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain to maintain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.48,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like if you just twitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And frankly, it isn't in fashion right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:58.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys run their mouth off about liking long hair on women...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:03.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but do they have any idea how much\Ntime, effort, and money it takes to maintain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.02,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.11,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're talking about yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:01.69,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.57,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're not in character anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.70,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're no longer Akira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.66,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:06.45,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:07.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And nobody ever notices your efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:14.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As for what would Akira look like with pigtails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:18.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find out more on our homepage or the radio show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Both hands will be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}I made a funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.26,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Then please look forward to next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:28.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By attitude, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep cutting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:33.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That upset about getting burned in the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I just figured nobody would recognize cowabunga now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:39.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:39.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:40.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:41.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we start over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:42.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:42.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:44.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they're holding an audition for Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first I've heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can try out if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:47.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Try out? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:48.51,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:49.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm actually him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:51.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:57.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's an anime song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:02.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in many different voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing anime songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is all about staying true to the original song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:11.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna sing, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:16.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The title was displayed earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, you don't know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:23.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you aren't any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:29.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:32.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you watching the series with me a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:33.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I still prefer the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:37.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an old geezer or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:47.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:51.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis is the best singer out of us sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:26.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:29.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Week...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:33.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...was apparently derived from industry lingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:36.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the period when movie ticket sales are extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:36.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace Shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:39.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time!
