Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.33,ls_keitai,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\frz350.973\pos(714,386)}H i i r a g i
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:42.10,ls_haiku,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(300,0)\pos(459,90)}My weight already
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:42.10,ls_haiku,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(300,0)\pos(459,121)}went all the way up in like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.10,ls_haiku,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(300,0)\pos(459,152)}the blink of an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:46.92,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell doesn't mean goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:54.01,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a long promise until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:23:03.02,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any regrets left in the place where our dreams were...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:09.95,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll only serve to chill your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:13.55,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:17.33,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,As many hours as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:23.92,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hold you in my arms.
